Hotel Starlight - Revenue Insights Dashboard

Welcome to the "Hotel Starlight - Revenue Insights Dashboard" project! This repository contains a comprehensive Power BI data analysis report 
for the fictional Hotel Starlight chain. The dashboard is designed to empower hotel managers with data-driven decision-making capabilities by
providing them with key revenue metrics and trends.

Project Overview
The "Hotel Starlight - Revenue Insights Dashboard" aims to offer detailed insights into the hotel's performance, focusing on revenue 
management and operational efficiency. 

Key features of this project include:

Data Transformation: Utilized Power Query for efficient data extraction, transformation, and loading (ETL).
Data Modeling: Created a robust data model to support complex calculations and visualizations.
Key Metrics: Developed 27 key metrics using DAX, including:
RevPAR (Revenue per Available Room)
ADR (Average Daily Rate)
Occupancy %
DSRN (Daily Sellable Room Nights)
DBRN (Daily Booked Room Nights)
DURN (Daily Utilized Room Nights)
Key Features
Metrics and Trends
Week-over-Week Trends: Calculated and visualized weekly trends to help managers track performance over time.
Weekend vs. Weekday Analysis: Built calculated columns using DAX to differentiate and analyze weekend (Friday and Saturday) versus weekday performance of key metrics.
Interactive Visualizations
Tooltips: Enhanced data points with additional contextual information.
Buttons: Incorporated buttons for easy navigation and interactivity.
Slicers: Added slicers to allow users to filter data based on various dimensions, enhancing the user experience and engagement.
